attributionInfo.brokerName: John L Scott Real Estate Grants Pass
John L Scott Real Estate Grants Pass

data.description: If you want a beautiful tranquil spot to sit and enjoy morning or night, you will love this piece of heaven! This .41 acre has a lot to offer with the beautiful trees, foilage and blackberries that surround the creek in your backyard. The bridge leads to an aviary that can be used for ducks and/or chickens. There is a nice walking trail right behind the fence line for your afternoon walks. Plenty of outbuildings are on this property to store your belongings as well as an older manufactured dwelling with an attached structure that has electricity and can be used for storage or as an extra dwelling unit. Several raised garden beds can be used for all your gardening desires. The remaining balance of the Sellers loan is assumable at 5.25% interest rate upon Buyer's approval. The remainder of the balance will have to be provided by Buyer's approval of a second loan or Seller may accept an owner carry option on that portion of the loan with an acceptable down payment and interest rate.
